Author: CloudySideDown
Text: Anyone who will like you or not solely based on your weight isnt worth the breath to say hello to. Hobby's are a good way to meet new people with similar interests. And something like a biking or running club could also help with not liking your body.

Author: vanillapie__
Text: I feel like this is true for me, like there's no way someone can like me when I'm fat like this :(
